## Add an Annotation


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![](week-6.2_files/figure-revealjs/annotation1-1.png){width=960}
:::
:::


## 

First step, add a horizontal line using `geom_hline()`... 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true"}
flfp_line + 
  geom_hline(yintercept = 52, linetype="dashed", color = "red", size = 1) 
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](week-6.2_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=960}
:::
:::


## 

Second step, the annotation with `annotate()`...


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true"}
flfp_line + 
  geom_hline(yintercept = 52, linetype="dashed", color = "red", size = 1) +
  annotate("text", x = 1995, y = 55, label = "Global average")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](week-6.2_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-9-1.png){width=960}
:::
:::


## Vertical Reference Line


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![](week-6.2_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-10-1.png){width=960}
:::
:::


## 

First step, add a horizontal line using `geom_hline()`... 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true"}
flfp_line + 
  geom_vline(xintercept=2020, linetype = "dashed", size = 1)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](week-6.2_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-11-1.png){width=960}
:::
:::


## 

Second step, add the annotation with `annotate()`


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true"}
flfp_line + 
  geom_vline(xintercept=2020, linetype = "dashed", size = 1) +
  annotate("text", x = 2017, y = 35, label = "Pandemic")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](week-6.2_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png){width=960}
:::
:::


